At whether we're in the congregation or in the family,

00:11:04.470 --> 00:11:07.629
we can be confident that if we sow peace,

00:11:07.629 --> 00:11:11.669
we will reap peace even if others don't respond.

00:11:11.669 --> 00:11:12.789
How?

